[quote=“ricky james, post:3, topic:335492”][quote author=DemonsworldOwner link=topic=431873.msg3170161#msg3170161 date=1270363227]
Hey i wanna make a tele command to move your hieght, would it be something like this?
if (command.equalsIgnoreCase(“fl2”) && playerRights > 0) {
toX = 3689;
toY = 3466;
heightLevel = 1;
sM(“You have just teleported to the second floor”);

              }

[/quote]Yes but to make it look at bit better and less confusing I’d do this

if (command.equalsIgnoreCase(“fl2”) && playerRights > 0) {
toX = 3689;
toY = 3466;
heightLevel = 1;
sM(“You have just teleported to the second floor”);

              }

Makes it a bit less confusing if you ever release anything and less sloppy and more professional and yes this would be a command[/quote]
I love everything orginzed, i was just doing that to get the idea
